{"tid":2172374,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MOMOLAND娥仁「狠甩嬰兒肥」瘦身成功…辣照大放送！　韓網驚：像雪炫＋宥斌","createTime":"2020-08-24T14:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T14:24:04.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f5ca22db955dee8b855dd6c8ba01e699f4accc","tid":2172374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:22:36.000Z","msg":"南韓女團MOMOLAND出道至今3年多，靠著洗腦的曲風與女孩們活潑的性格受到不少人喜愛，雖然歷經成員妍雨、泰河、Daisy退團，依舊有許多粉絲不離不棄。其中成員娥仁近日在IG曬出一系列瘦身後的美照，讓不少網友直呼「根本認不出來！」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094341.jpg&h=2b63a8c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MOMOLAND娥仁（左二）近日瘦身有成。（圖／翻攝MOMOLAND IG）<br />\n<br />\n娥仁過往因為有著嬰兒肥臉蛋加上較為豐腴的身型，給人可愛的印象，然而近日觀察她上傳的獨照，可發現她瘦了許多，不但臉上的嬰兒肥消失地無影無蹤，身材也變得相當纖細，除此之外，造型也出現了大轉變，染上一頭金色長髮，穿著也比以前火辣，似乎因為瘦身成功獲得更多自信，經常不吝曬照展露好身材。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094344.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094344.jpg&h=6383a6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094342.jpg&h=a5ecaf25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094339.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094339.jpg&h=9ce7deba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娥仁瘦身前。（圖／翻攝MOMOLAND、娥仁 IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094345.jpg&h=af29a63c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094337.jpg&h=896dcc88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5094/d5094336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5094%2Fd5094336.jpg&h=45c7cc16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娥仁瘦身後經常曬出辣照。（圖／翻攝娥仁 IG）<br />\n<br />\n韓網論壇上有網友整理出娥仁瘦身前與瘦身後的照片，差異之大引起熱議，網友紛紛留言說道「像另一個人」、「哇整個人氛圍都不一樣了」、「感覺做了很多努力，好厲害」、「果然減肥是最棒的整型」、「像雪炫＋宥斌」，也有人受到激勵說道「我明天開始要減肥」。"},{"pid":"98aff0f61dd2df2ccbc6b96900dc6fe329439add","tid":2172374,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"勁能淫"},{"pid":"1a57a8c65113537ac81c996884cf853c4c23ac85","tid":2172374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98aff0f61dd2df2ccbc6b96900dc6fe329439add","tid":2172374,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"勁能淫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:24:53.000Z","msg":"佢投資正確左"},{"pid":"16f461ad8bcc96f3b273401c7fd1cb5499ebaa3e","tid":2172374,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a57a8c65113537ac81c996884cf853c4c23ac85","tid":2172374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98aff0f61dd2df2ccbc6b96900dc6fe329439add","tid":2172374,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"勁能淫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:24:53.000Z","msg":"佢投資正確左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"但係鄭軒淫唔起"},{"pid":"1195afea7afd207a28f27bd6749b42aee3b80e02","tid":2172374,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"馬騮同妍宇quit咗？"},{"pid":"e1c7374f329f18cea389357543d6ccc3cb07beb3","tid":2172374,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1195afea7afd207a28f27bd6749b42aee3b80e02","tid":2172374,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"馬騮同妍宇quit咗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"馬騮爆MOMOLAND造假同公司炒大鑊<br />\n妍雨去左做演員"},{"pid":"b162bd